      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "27d4faf293:74",
      "text": "选择 job graph 中当前所选 task 的父 task。",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "27d4faf293:81",
      "text": "如果系统已配置为 archive job，则 job context menu 会显示",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "27d4faf293:85",
      "text": "。要查看 archived job，请按 job list 顶部的 current/archived 按钮，使 archived 高亮。对 archived job 唯一可执行的操作是 restore，它会取消归档该 job，并将其移回当前 job 集合。",
